273
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:41,790
Stop!

274
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,112
When you play the rod, be flexible!

275
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,516
Senior.

276
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,035
Forget it.

277
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,670
Why?

278
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:20,270
Since Uncle Chen agrees the acquisition,

279
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,919
Why should we fight?

280
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,274
Anyway, we may not sure win.

281
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,873
If we aren't confident, why go for the race?

282
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,195
I'll study hard.

283
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,759
We may not lose in the race.

284
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:30,353
You are so proud of yourself, aren't you?

285
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:31,913
Working hard isn't a matter,

286
