287
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,116
I want everyone to know that...

288
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:37,555
Our school can overcome this challenge.

289
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:39,598
Now the school is okay, isn't it?

290
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:42,637
A big commercial group is going to acquire us.

291
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:45,872
