international races, isn't that great?

292
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:51,916
Jie, it's you who should consider, not me.

293
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,428
Go back and think about it.

294
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,709
Senior.

295
00:22:03,040 --> 00:22:05,315
You must consider the reputation of Choyleefut.

296
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:17,359
The sponsor of this competition...

297
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:19,596
Chiguo Air-conditioner sponsors 10 million.

298
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,876
Yi-fung Group sponsors 8 million.

299
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:24,076
Tai-cheong Trading sponsors 5 million.

300
00:22:24,360 --> 00:22:26,237
The total money from the sponsors...

301
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,879
It has already reached 58 million.

302
00:22:28,320 --> 00:22:31,392
Good, you've got a great record
just on the first day.

303
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:32,510
It's really a miracle.

304
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:33,750
30 million out of the total sum
of money is because of...

305
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:36,633
our martial arts consultant, Mr. Zuo Zhang-hong.

306
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:39,954
We have to keep working hard.

307
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:42,753
Before the competition, our target is 80 million.

308
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:43,756
Yes.

309
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:55,794
Hubby, come and try it.

310
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:58,798
I bought you a big and sweet water melon.

311
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:04,994
Honey, this is as sweet as you.

312
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:08,789
Cut the crap and eat your fruit!

313
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:13,358
Well, I think you have something to tell me.

314
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:15,552
Should I tell you anything?

315
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:18,434
Someone told me that the school is to be acquired.

316
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,868
Is it true?

317
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:22,713
Come on, don't be nosy.

318
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:25,994
You don't love me now.

319
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:27,599
I don't want to talk to you!
You don't love me now.

320
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:29,955
Honey...

321
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:32,515
Don't get mad, okay, I'll tell you.

322
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,957
Actually I don't know the details
of the acquisition.

323
