It's because Uncle said yes already.

324
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:40,239
But Jie disagrees.

325
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:43,353
So they are going to have a competition
one month later,

326
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,511
Each side will have 3 fighters
to join the competition.

327
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:47,711
The winner will have the final say.

328
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:51,153
So, there must be some good prizes
for the competition, right?

329
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:53,675
Say, how about any money award?

330
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,592
I am not sure about that.

331
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:57,632
You're stupid!

332
00:23:57,800 --> 00:23:59,119
Why don't you ask?

333
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,508
I am not asking...

334
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:05,151
You don't love me now.

335
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,589
You don't love me now!

336
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,829
You don't love me at all.

337
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,037
Where are you taking the water melon to?

338
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:12,995
Welcome.

339
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:14,990
My friend is over there.

340
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,159
I didn't expect you come for the contract.

341
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,992
Are you scared? You still have time
to change your mind.

342
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,592
Yes, I am worried that...

343
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:32,070
If you lose, you'll lose face too.

344
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:35,989
Cut the crap!

345
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:37,998
You can take it back
and study well before signing.

346
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:47,989
Good terms!

347
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,718
The winner will get 3 million.

348
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:52,197
Pan-America International is always fair.

349
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:55,749
You'll get the reward which you have contributed.

350
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:13,788
Okay, I won't send you to the door.

351
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,394
Are you asking me to leave like this?

352
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,395
So, what do you want?

353
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,918
At least you can buy me a drink.

354
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:24,955
I've got a date.

355
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,755
If you want to drink, you can go to another table.

356
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,235
I'll pay the bill.

357
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:42,360
Take your time, I won't bother you dude.

358
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:57,592
Poor girl, how can she take a cool man
as her boyfriend?

359
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:00,956
Thank you for coming.

360
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:07,358
Uncle, what should we do about the competition?

361
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:12,349
