362
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,551
Ken and I will try our very best.

363
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,991
But the point is, we still need one more guy.

364
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,159
You really want to compete?

365
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:22,078
Have good practice first.

366
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,673
So start from the basic training first.

367
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,069
Start from the basic training?

368
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:27,118
We only have one month's time.

369
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:29,556
God has fixed everything.

370
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:33,637
If the 3rd one is going to show up,

371
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:35,392
He will show up at last.

372
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:38,872
Now, don't think anything about the competition.

373
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:41,717
Have some handstand practice now.

374
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:44,799
It will let you view from another angle.

375
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:14,156
What are you doing here?

376
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:15,275
Why are you here?

377
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,671
I paid the school fee,
so why can't I come to school?

378
00:27:21,040 --> 00:27:23,235
If you want to learn kung-fu, go for my senior.

379
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:26,354
We are now having secret training,
not open to visitors.

380
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:28,029
Secret training?

381
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,592
You mean handstand is part of
your secret training?

382
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:34,434
Be serious, otherwise, just give up.

383
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,836
By the way, I didn't say
I come for learning kung-fu.

384
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:39,359
I just come and walk around.

385
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:41,551
I like to stay wherever I want.

386
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,074
Are you falling for me?

387
00:27:55,080 --> 00:27:56,877
Leave her alone, let's keep on practicing.

388
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:57,990
Okay.

389
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:08,518
Another week has passed.

390
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:11,588
Senior hasn't promised to join us.

391
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:14,033
Until now, I am still confused that...

392
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,918
Why my dad wants to give up the school?

393
00:28:16,360 --> 00:28:17,395
What is his motive?

394
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:21,756
Can Ken and I get the last victory?

395
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,433
Why do you stay up this late?

396
00:29:01,640 --> 00:29:02,595
Master.

397
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,797
I just can't sleep.

398
00:29:07,040 --> 00:29:08,189
Do you want a chat?

399
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:10,630
Let's go.

400
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:14,951
Master, did I do a wrong thing?

401
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:19,752
Everyone has his own way of thinking.

402
00:29:20,120 --> 00:29:22,759
You can't say it right or wrong.

403
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:26,990
I don't join the competition,
it is for the good of the school.

404
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,628
Our school has a history of over a hundred year.

405
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,229
All the students from every generation...

406
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:35,198
They all want to contribute something new
for the good of the school.

407
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:37,875
I am the same.

408
00:29:39,520 --> 00:29:40,748
Let me ask you one question,

409
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:43,996
Do you love your wife?

410
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:44,950
Yes.

411
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:48,359
Will you dump your old lover...

412
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:49,748
Because of a new love?

413
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,989
Of course not.

414
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:56,430
It has a long history,
older the age, deeper in love.

415
00:29:58,280 --> 00:30:01,352
Go to sleep now, I have got to sleep too.

416
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:03,395
Good night, master.

417
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,189
Are you all right?

418
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,589
Miss Xia, I am sorry.

419
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:40,958
Jie, take her over there and take a rest.

420
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:42,590
Come on.

421
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:49,073
Be careful...

422
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,755
Does it hurt?

423
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:57,115
How about this?

424
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,797
Does it hurt?

425
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,432
Not that serious, just a slight twist only.

426
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:05,433
It'll be all right soon.

427
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,070
I really appreciate that!

428
00:31:07,280 --> 00:31:08,872
You don't come for learning kungfu,

429
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:10,268
But why do you come here everyday?

430
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,672
And, this is not your office.

431
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:17,559
Please don't wear high heel shoes
here again, okay?

432
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,949
None of your business!

433
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:25,515
You're okay now.

434
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:28,997
When you're home, put some ice
on the wound to comfort it.

435
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,875
Wait for me.

436
00:31:42,840 --> 00:31:44,239
What are these shoes for?

437
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:47,631
Do you think we have high heel shoes for you?

438
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:49,230
You still have a choice,

439
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,396
Either leave here without shoes,

440
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,113
Or, you can wear these soft shoes.

441
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,150
Are they okay?

442
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,109
They don't match!

443
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:10,113
Look at you guys!

444
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:12,039
Look at your pose! It's poor!

445
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,235
You don't show any strength at all.

446
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:15,750
If I don't join you guys,
how can you win the race?

447
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,750
Wait!

448
00:34:17,040 --> 00:34:18,268
Senior, what did you say?

449
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:20,278
Can't you hear my words?

450
00:34:20,680 --> 00:34:22,989
Without me, how can you guys win?

451
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,119
He means he wants to fight.

452
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:30,110
Look at you! How can you practice like this?

453
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:32,191
My master just doesn't want to make any comments!

454
00:34:32,520 --> 00:34:34,158
Master, please say something fair,

455
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:35,919
If I don't join them,

456
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:38,076
Will they have any chance to win

457
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,718
See? Remember what I told you?

458
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:44,837
The third one will show up sooner or later.

459
00:34:46,160 --> 00:34:47,275
You have heard what master said, haven't you?

460
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:49,078
I am so important! Work hard, men!

461
00:34:49,240 --> 00:34:50,878
Master, please say something fair.

462
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:52,678
I can't hear your words, please say again.

463
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:53,795
This is great!

464
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:10,312
Si-hai is weird today.

465
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:12,679
He doesn't want to join the race, does he?

466
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:15,151
Why does he practice so hard now?

467
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,108
It's hot! It's hot!

468
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:22,598
Si-hai is practicing under such hot weather.

469
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:25,400
He would definitely stink when he is home.

470
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:29,675
Do you agree with him to join the competition?

471
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:31,796
Sure, I am supporting!

472
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:37,956
They will have an award of 3 million if they win.

473
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:40,988
3 million!

474
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:45,633
Si-hai, work hard...

475
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,756
Hubby, I love you!

476
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:51,069
