479
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,798
- Aren't you satisfied?
- Excuse me.

480
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:01,630
Go practice!

481
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:09,032
She is so cute!

482
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:12,956
Master, is she Jie's girlfriend?

483
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:18,073
Master, is there something wrong with your eyes?

484
00:36:18,720 --> 00:36:20,233
Do you need some eye-drops?

485
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:30,114
This is great! You look better now.

486
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,395
Do you think this is nice?

487
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:35,358
Have you changed because of me?

488
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:39,228
Come on! I came here for you.

489
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:41,072
Please come to my office at 3 tomorrow.

490
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,389
I'll show you something.

491
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:45,431
I know you would date me sooner or later.

492
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:50,110
Tomorrow at 3pm, don't be late.

493
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:51,316
I am leaving.

494
00:36:52,080 --> 00:36:53,274
See you tomorrow.

495
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,953
Hi, I have an appointment with Xia Yu-fai,
my name is Jie Chen.

496
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,639
All right, please wait.

497
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:15,316
The appointment is 3 o'clock in the afternoon.

498
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:16,990
I came early.

499
00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:19,198
Please go over there and take a seat.

500
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,952
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

501
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,355
Who is he?

502
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:35,437
He doesn't seem to be our colleague.

503
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:50,436
You came early.

504
00:38:50,720 --> 00:38:51,789
I seldom be late.

505
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:55,111
I'd like to let you visit...

506
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:57,236
the training process of the
Pan-America International Group.

507
00:38:57,600 --> 00:38:58,510
Are you interested?

508
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,389
Let's go.

509
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:57,915
How do you feel?

510
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:16,910
Have you eaten yet?

511
00:40:24,520 --> 00:40:25,669
Harder please.

512
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:28,310
Jie, where have you been?

513
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:30,039
You are so serious about this competition,
aren't you?

514
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:31,036
Do you have to practice?

515
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,679
What's up? What's happened?

516
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:35,071
What's wrong with your hand?
Fighting with someone?

517
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:57,317
This is the difference between our trainings.

518
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:59,312
Hitting the metal balls and sand bags.

519
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:02,713
It will ruin your hands for sure!

520
00:41:03,240 --> 00:41:05,356
For karate players, we also have similar practice.

521
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,870
That's why the lethality of karate is stunning.

522
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:09,632
The punch's speed is fast and strong.

523
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:11,598
Actually you are a great karate player,

524
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,637
Why do you want to learn Choyleefut?

525
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:20,111
This is all because of my grandfather.

526
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,988
In the thirteenth year of Taisho,

527
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:31,637
My grandfather was the bodyguard
of a senior official.

528
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,195
This senior official of Japan...

529
00:41:33,560 --> 00:41:36,120
Once helped a Chinese named Sun.

530
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:38,319
Because of a chance,

531
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:42,315
My grandfather met the bodyguard
of that Chinese man.

532
00:41:43,200 --> 00:41:46,590
They appreciated each other
and learnt martial arts from each other.

533
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:49,554
At last, the kung-fu of that Chinese bodyguard...

534
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:51,671
Impressed my grand-father very much.

535
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:53,955
My grandfather lost,

536
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:57,830
But what impressed him not
because of the guy's kung-fu,

537
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,236
But also the ethics.

538
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:01,512
Because of that chance,

539
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:03,875
It brought him a new face of Bushido spirit.

540
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:07,638
That is a stage which karate player
can never reach.

541
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:12,115
Later, my grandfather finally knew that,

542
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:16,599
That kind of kung-fu is named Choyleefut.

543
00:42:17,120 --> 00:42:19,793
At last, they became buddies.

544
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:21,992
The greatest wish of my grandfather was...

545
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:24,390
He wanted to learn Choyleefut.

546
00:42:25,640 --> 00:42:26,959
What a pity that he has got no chance.

547
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:30,235
So I want to come to China to learn Choyleefut.

548
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:33,154
It is to make my grandfather's wish come true.

549
00:42:34,720 --> 00:42:38,235
You came for Choyleefut
because of your grandfather!

550
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,950
Not exactly.

551
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:44,157
Actually I love kung-fu.

552
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,952
Sure, I can tell.

553
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:53,949
Now, it's time for me to teach you guys.

554
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:57,313
Actually, every school has its own strength.

555
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,912
Take Choyleefut as an example.

556
00:43:00,080 --> 00:43:01,308
We fight with techniques.

557
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:05,274
In our fights, punch, kick, bump, push,
pick and jump...

558
00:43:05,520 --> 00:43:07,272
They are ever changing.

559
00:43:07,560 --> 00:43:10,313
Even you have strong punches and strong kicks,

560
00:43:10,520 --> 00:43:12,431
If you can't hit me, it's useless.

561
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:15,996
But if you are hit by me instead,

562
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:18,748
Possibly some bones will be broken at last.

563
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:22,993
What if you are punched first?

564
00:43:23,160 --> 00:43:25,879
Isn't it possible?

565
00:43:26,840 --> 00:43:28,990
Tell me, tell me...

566
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:30,794
How can I get punched?

567
00:43:33,360 --> 00:43:35,078
- What's up?
- Go...

568
00:43:35,240 --> 00:43:36,434
Uncle, don't ask now.

569
00:43:36,640 --> 00:43:37,834
What do you want?

570
00:43:38,560 --> 00:43:40,915
Take this spicy goose leg, come on.

571
00:43:41,760 --> 00:43:42,556
Some wine too.

572
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:45,117
These are my favorites!

573
00:43:45,600 --> 00:43:48,319
Uncle, can you teach us now?

574
00:43:50,720 --> 00:43:53,678
Because of these food and wine,

575
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:55,029
I will teach you anything you ask for.

576
00:43:57,160 --> 00:43:58,354
Uncle, you promised!

577
00:43:59,040 --> 00:43:59,870
What's up?

578
00:44:00,360 --> 00:44:01,395
Teach us something really powerful.

579
00:44:01,760 --> 00:44:03,637
Well, nothing is really powerful!

580
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:06,319
I mean the most powerful stance of Choyleefut!

581
00:44:06,520 --> 00:44:07,839
No powerful stance at all!

582
00:44:08,160 --> 00:44:10,151
It's not like novels!

583
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:13,277
Uncle, why do you eat up the food then?

584
00:44:14,240 --> 00:44:16,037
Isn't it for greeting your uncle?

585
00:44:20,520 --> 00:44:21,953
Don't be disappointed.

586
00:44:22,520 --> 00:44:24,078
I have fixed everything.

587
00:44:24,360 --> 00:44:26,590
Tomorrow, you will have a new kind of training.

588
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:29,069
Sure you will find them interesting and funny.

589
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:40,910
You lost, it's your turn.

590
00:44:41,600 --> 00:44:42,396
Go!

591
00:44:45,600 --> 00:44:47,750
Uncle, we have stood here for half day.

592
00:44:47,920 --> 00:44:48,750
What are we waiting for?

593
00:44:49,760 --> 00:44:52,752
Yes, I think you're wasting our time.

594
00:44:53,080 --> 00:44:54,513
I am waiting for your question!

595
00:44:56,840 --> 00:45:00,389
Actually you are not psychologically ready yet.

596
00:45:00,600 --> 00:45:03,239
What do you mean?

597
00:45:03,600 --> 00:45:05,113
Let's take an example.

598
00:45:05,320 --> 00:45:08,118
If you have a doubt unsolved,

599
00:45:08,520 --> 00:45:10,988
can you learn something whole-heartedly?

600
00:45:11,400 --> 00:45:12,958
I don't quite understand.

601
00:45:17,280 --> 00:45:18,872
Come on, come and hit me.

602
00:45:26,160 --> 00:45:26,956
Again.

603
00:45:33,840 --> 00:45:35,956
Jie, Si-hai, what have you seen?

604
00:45:36,120 --> 00:45:37,109
You are fast.

605
00:45:37,800 --> 00:45:39,028
I am not fast.

606
00:45:39,600 --> 00:45:42,068
I just know what you guys will act.

607
00:45:43,600 --> 00:45:45,113
When you meet your rival,

608
00:45:45,360 --> 00:45:48,591
When they already know how you act,

609
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:52,833
You'd act something which you don't even predict.

610
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:56,675
This will then confuse your rival.

611
00:45:56,840 --> 00:45:57,909
Do you guys understand?

612
00:45:58,560 --> 00:45:59,231
I am asking you!

613
00:45:59,400 --> 00:46:07,080
Go...

614
00:46:14,400 --> 00:46:15,196
Hello?

615
00:46:15,520 --> 00:46:16,396
Staying up late?

616
00:46:16,760 --> 00:46:20,070
It's early now, how is your practice?

617
00:46:20,720 --> 00:46:21,835
I am not used to that.

618
00:46:22,240 --> 00:46:23,195
Why?

619
00:46:23,640 --> 00:46:26,074
I am not used to not seeing you
for one whole week.

620
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:33,634
What do you want?

621
00:46:33,880 --> 00:46:35,552
I will be off 2 days later.

622
00:46:35,880 --> 00:46:37,552
Can you apply for a leave?

623
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:38,789
I'd like to have some fun with you.

624
00:46:42,280 --> 00:46:44,032
"The birthday of Zuo Zhang-hong"

625
00:46:44,240 --> 00:46:47,312
But I have an appointment in the afternoon,
I am only free in the morning.

626
00:46:47,720 --> 00:46:50,632
Great, no problem, I'll come and pick you up.

627
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:52,756
Okay.

628
00:46:52,960 --> 00:46:54,916
- Okay, bye!
- Bye!

629
00:47:03,720 --> 00:47:08,589
Hubby, I checked with the property agent today.

630
00:47:09,320 --> 00:47:11,151
There is a nice flat around.

631
00:47:11,360 --> 00:47:13,874
With a sitting room and a living room,
just costs 800 thousand.

632
00:47:14,040 --> 00:47:15,075
What for?

633
00:47:15,440 --> 00:47:16,350
I check it for you.

634
00:47:16,600 --> 00:47:17,589
I've got no money to buy any flat.

635
00:47:19,240 --> 00:47:21,071
If you win, you will have money then.

636
00:47:21,760 --> 00:47:23,830
That is the money for the school, not for me.

637
00:47:25,080 --> 00:47:26,559
You risk your life for the school!

638
00:47:26,720 --> 00:47:28,756
If you win, why will the money go to the school?

639
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:31,912
I fight for the name of the school.

640
00:47:32,240 --> 00:47:35,312
If there is any award,
it sure will go to the school.

641
00:47:37,960 --> 00:47:41,077
You don't want a baby.

642
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:45,071
You don't want us to move out.

643
00:47:45,240 --> 00:47:46,798
You just want to live here
to take care of your master.

644
00:47:46,960 --> 00:47:49,713
Okay, I just listened to you!

645
00:47:51,240 --> 00:47:53,071
The truth is, you don't have a penny!

646
00:47:53,720 --> 00:47:56,837
But have you thought of my feeling?

647
00:47:58,040 --> 00:47:59,359
Until now,

648
00:47:59,560 --> 00:48:01,551
I have no youth, I have no family.

649
00:48:01,720 --> 00:48:05,349
I have nothing! I...

650
00:48:10,640 --> 00:48:12,995
You don't love me now, you don't love me!

651
00:48:36,640 --> 00:48:37,629
What time is it now?

652
00:48:47,160 --> 00:48:49,310
Do you know you are one minute late?

653
00:48:50,840 --> 00:48:52,512
One minute may not be important to you.

654
00:48:52,680 --> 00:48:54,238
But this is very important to me.

655
00:48:54,400 --> 00:48:55,628
No, it's about the car...

656
00:48:55,960 --> 00:48:57,951
All right, it's my fault, you are right.

657
00:48:58,120 --> 00:48:59,439
Sorry, don't get mad!

658
00:49:07,400 --> 00:49:08,992
Move now. What's up?

659
00:49:09,680 --> 00:49:10,635
Buckle up please.

660
00:50:20,560 --> 00:50:22,278
Miss Xia hasn't come back yet.

661
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:25,436
It's all right, I'll be here waiting.

662
00:50:25,680 --> 00:50:27,238
All right, please help yourself.

663
00:51:59,560 --> 00:52:00,356
What's up?

664
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:08,876
Give it to me...

665
00:52:16,840 --> 00:52:19,877
Give it back to me...

666
00:52:41,040 --> 00:52:44,316
Jie, you signed the contract with our group,

667
00:52:44,560 --> 00:52:47,597
Isn't it wrong for me to stay this close to you?

668
00:52:47,800 --> 00:52:49,233
What did you say?

669
00:52:49,600 --> 00:52:51,318
Come on, this is our personal time.

670
00:52:52,760 --> 00:52:54,591
Look at the beautiful sun!

671
00:53:11,000 --> 00:53:13,195
Here you are. Have an early rest.

672
00:54:03,080 --> 00:54:04,115
Have you forgotten?

673
00:54:05,000 --> 00:54:08,117
I am sorry, I know today is your birthday.

674
00:54:08,280 --> 00:54:09,713
No need to say sorry to me.

675
00:54:11,080 --> 00:54:13,833
I have always told myself...

676
00:54:14,240 --> 00:54:16,993
I'll be happy if you are happy.

677
00:54:17,840 --> 00:54:19,910
If you enjoy two men wooing you at the same time,

678
00:54:21,280 --> 00:54:22,679
I am willing to take it.

679
00:54:24,040 --> 00:54:25,314
Please don't say that.

680
00:54:44,080 --> 00:54:46,150
Guys, listen, the three masters here...

681
00:54:46,320 --> 00:54:49,676
They are from different schools of martial arts.

682
00:54:49,960 --> 00:54:53,396
This is master Dongjia from Thailand,
he plays Thai Boxing

683
00:54:54,560 --> 00:54:57,632
This is Master Liu, a master of Hong Style

684
00:54:58,320 --> 00:55:01,278
And this is Master Li, a Tai-chi Master.

685
00:55:02,840 --> 00:55:05,400
Master, do you want us to learn from them?

686
00:55:05,960 --> 00:55:07,359
Not learning.

687
00:55:07,680 --> 00:55:09,511
- You'll be hit by them.
- What?

688
00:55:10,040 --> 00:55:13,191
Just defense, no attack.

689
00:55:23,320 --> 00:55:24,878
If you guys want to win,

690
00:55:25,040 --> 00:55:27,315
First you need to know how to be defeated.

691
00:55:27,920 --> 00:55:31,276
Experience will help you grow.

692
00:55:43,720 --> 00:55:47,235
More fights, more chances to win.

693
00:57:46,120 --> 00:57:47,599
Uncle, why don't you go to sleep?

694
00:57:48,200 --> 00:57:50,668
It's not time to sleep.

695
00:57:51,880 --> 00:57:53,393
Uncle, you haven't changed at all.

696
00:57:53,600 --> 00:57:54,749
Your words are always funny.

697
00:57:56,160 --> 00:57:58,310
Come on, you don't know
how to rub your wound at all.

698
00:57:58,520 --> 00:57:59,589
Let me help you.

699
00:57:59,920 --> 00:58:00,716
Thank you.

700
00:58:05,800 --> 00:58:08,712
Have your father given you any call?

701
00:58:09,360 --> 00:58:11,828
Nope. He seems to have disappeared!

702
00:58:12,000 --> 00:58:13,353
I called him several times,
he just didn't answer the call.

703
00:58:13,560 --> 00:58:14,515
Has he called you?

704
00:58:15,440 --> 00:58:16,873
I have no phone.

705
00:58:18,240 --> 00:58:19,878
What's up? Are you missing him?

706
00:58:22,040 --> 00:58:25,077
Yes, but...

707
00:58:25,920 --> 00:58:27,239
I don't miss him everyday.

708
00:58:31,880 --> 00:58:35,270
When a kung-fu master has reached certain stage,

709
00:58:35,640 --> 00:58:38,029
It's really hard for him to find a matched rival.

710
00:58:39,520 --> 00:58:42,034
Your father is the same.

711
00:59:51,200 --> 00:59:54,795
Hey, you read your father's letter,

712
00:59:54,960 --> 00:59:56,154
What did he wrote?

713
00:59:57,160 --> 00:59:59,799
He wrote many things,
and he mentioned your name too.

714
01:00:00,680 --> 01:00:03,194
So, what is it about?

715
01:00:04,240 --> 01:00:05,593
Okay, I can tell you,

716
01:00:05,800 --> 01:00:06,949
But you have to tell me one thing first.

717
01:00:07,120 --> 01:00:09,315
Why did my dad leave here alone for his world?

718
01:00:09,520 --> 01:00:11,078
And you have stayed behind?

719
01:00:24,760 --> 01:00:25,749
Junior.

720
01:00:26,200 --> 01:00:28,998
There is another world outside,
do you want to go with me?

721
01:00:29,520 --> 01:00:31,078
I think it's shapeless and illusive!

722
01:00:31,560 --> 01:00:33,790
As an old Chinese saying,
better take a solid step.

723
01:00:34,000 --> 01:00:35,752
Do you really want to go along the stream?

724
01:00:37,160 --> 01:00:39,390
At least I can view it.

725
01:00:39,840 --> 01:00:40,955
Different people have different wills.

726
01:00:41,360 --> 01:00:43,669
Well, let's walk our own way.

727
01:00:44,400 --> 01:00:45,992
But every roads lead to Rome.

728
01:00:48,960 --> 01:00:50,393
It's like a novel!

729
01:00:54,720 --> 01:00:55,755
I've got it, Uncle,

730
01:00:55,920 --> 01:00:58,229
You intentionally let my dad choose going abroad.

731
01:00:59,120 --> 01:01:01,031
It's because I don't know English.

732
01:01:01,240 --> 01:01:02,639
Come on, stop pretending!

733
01:01:06,440 --> 01:01:09,193
Uncle, for this competition,

734
01:01:09,360 --> 01:01:10,554
Do you think we have a chance to win?

735
01:01:11,760 --> 01:01:13,159
The path is under your feet,

736
01:01:13,320 --> 01:01:15,993
You'd choose your own path and walk.

737
01:01:16,920 --> 01:01:19,912
Okay, I'll pick the stream as you did.

738
01:01:20,080 --> 01:01:21,718
And I'll guard this old pond.

739
01:01:23,360 --> 01:01:24,759
All right, thank you, Uncle.

740
01:01:25,080 --> 01:01:26,957
I am going to sleep now, good night.

741
01:01:30,600 --> 01:01:34,275
Jie, but you haven't told me
what your dad wrote about me.

742
01:01:34,920 --> 01:01:36,751
I just lied, he said nothing about you.

743
01:01:37,000 --> 01:01:37,796
Goodnight!

744
01:01:55,800 --> 01:01:58,155
Jie, I'd like to talk to you.

745
01:01:58,320 --> 01:01:59,435
I am downstairs.

746
01:02:15,160 --> 01:02:16,036
Hey!

747
01:02:17,960 --> 01:02:18,915
What's up?

748
01:02:27,640 --> 01:02:29,949
Come on, why do you pull a long face?

749
01:02:31,640 --> 01:02:34,598
About the competition tomorrow, just work hard!

750
01:02:34,760 --> 01:02:37,877
What's up? Are you mad at me?

751
01:02:43,840 --> 01:02:45,956
Stop! Stop!

752
01:02:47,640 --> 01:02:48,390
What do you mean?

753
01:02:49,640 --> 01:02:50,675
Get lost!

754
01:02:51,880 --> 01:02:53,359
I think we should not meet again.

755
01:03:22,680 --> 01:03:24,955
Yu-fai, about the relationship
between you and Jie,

756
01:03:25,120 --> 01:03:27,076
It will affect the result of the competition.

757
01:03:27,440 --> 01:03:28,589
It's up to your decision.

758
01:03:29,280 --> 01:03:30,872
Yes, boss.

759
01:04:16,240 --> 01:04:17,355
I really regret...

760
01:04:17,560 --> 01:04:19,630
I regret not treasuring the minute
which I stayed with you.

761
01:04:34,080 --> 01:04:36,275
If God could spare that minute to me again,

762
01:04:36,960 --> 01:04:38,313
I think, this minute...

763
01:04:38,640 --> 01:04:41,552
This minute would have become
the most precious minute in my life.

764
01:04:55,960 --> 01:04:56,949
Sister-in-law.

765
01:04:59,120 --> 01:05:00,553
You'd press with skills!

766
01:05:00,720 --> 01:05:02,119
Let me do it. You'd better go out.

767
01:05:02,280 --> 01:05:03,633
Let's get out now.

768
01:05:11,000 --> 01:05:12,718
Honey, I am sorry.

769
01:05:12,880 --> 01:05:13,869
I am sorry!

770
01:05:15,560 --> 01:05:18,870
I haven't heard that word for years.

771
01:05:19,800 --> 01:05:21,074
Do you know why?

772
01:05:22,520 --> 01:05:25,751
It's because my hubby is an honest guy.

773
01:05:26,120 --> 01:05:29,396
He hasn't done anything wrong to his wife.

774
01:05:31,800 --> 01:05:33,791
But his wife...

775
01:05:33,960 --> 01:05:37,236
His wife has sometimes pushed him
to do something beyond his wish.

776
01:05:38,080 --> 01:05:39,035
Come on!

777
01:05:39,560 --> 01:05:41,232
What my wife wants me to do...

778
01:05:41,440 --> 01:05:43,078
Is what I want to do!

779
01:05:43,720 --> 01:05:44,596
Got it.

780
01:05:45,560 --> 01:05:46,515
Well,

781
01:05:49,040 --> 01:05:51,793
I heard that your rivals are tough guys.

782
01:05:51,960 --> 01:05:53,029
Can you win?

783
01:05:53,320 --> 01:05:55,151
I worry that you'd get hurt.

784
01:05:55,320 --> 01:05:57,151
Why not put it this way, I'll talk to your master,

785
01:05:57,320 --> 01:05:58,275
I'll tell him that you'd quit.

786
01:05:58,440 --> 01:05:59,429
Who am I?

787
01:06:00,200 --> 01:06:01,633
- You're Si-hai.
- That's right.

788
01:06:01,920 --> 01:06:04,832
I am the senior, I will never lose.

789
01:06:05,280 --> 01:06:08,636
You'd better go out and view my show.

790
01:06:09,000 --> 01:06:09,955
Okay?

791
01:06:27,200 --> 01:06:28,349
Senior, let's go.

792
01:06:29,680 --> 01:06:31,159
The competition is about to start now.

793
01:06:31,680 --> 01:06:32,715
Are you ready?

794
01:06:34,520 --> 01:06:35,714
I will sure win.

795
01:06:36,920 --> 01:06:38,638
I believe that you'll win too.

796
01:06:41,120 --> 01:06:44,078
After the race, I'll go back to Japan.

797
01:06:44,520 --> 01:06:45,509
Why do you leave in such a hurry?

798
01:06:46,040 --> 01:06:47,792
I'd like to pay a visit to my grandfather's grave.

799
01:06:48,240 --> 01:06:50,390
I want to tell him that
I've learnt the authentic Choyleefut!

800
01:06:51,240 --> 01:06:53,754
Sure! So, will you come back?

801
01:06:54,520 --> 01:06:55,509
Of course I will.

802
01:06:55,920 --> 01:06:57,558
I don't want to leave my buddy behind.

803
01:06:58,200 --> 01:07:00,077
- Come back as soon as possible.
- Sure.

804
01:07:09,400 --> 01:07:11,630
Ladies and gentlemen, how are you doing?

